Default parameter values

default_parameters.Rd

These are default parameter value objects for parameters that take a values argument. When optimizing over qualitative parameter values, you can subset the default arguments listed here and supply the result to values if you want to optimize a different set of values.

values_activation

values_prune_method

values_weight_func

values_surv_dist

values_weight_scheme

values_token

Format

A character vector of parameter values.
